        "title": "[api-minor] Remove the Webpack-only npm dependencies from `pdfjs-dist` (PR 11418 follow-up)",
        "user": {
            "login": "Snuffleupagus",
            "id": 2692120,
            "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI2OTIxMjA=",
